WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.633 --> 00:00:03.240
Good morning family, praise the Lord!

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:05.571
I'm glad you all joined me again today to pray.

00:00:05.571 --> 00:00:15.000
We have a lot of work to do actually, but I just want to give you all a testimony real quick about a lady who reached out to us for prayer.

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:27.195
She said she broke her hip and four ribs and was in a lot of pain.

00:00:39.103 --> 00:00:55.511
I prayed for her on this video right here, and she contacted us and told us, 'When you were praying and believing for my healing, I just want to let you know the Lord healed me.

00:00:55.511 --> 00:01:08.720
' I want to give all the glory, honor, and praise to the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:01:17.025 --> 00:01:19.119
He is the healer, and He is healing the sick, the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:01:19.119 --> 00:01:26.200
He is a good God and He is a healer.

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:40.560
That's why I have this shirt here; I want this to stand bold in black and white: 'Jesus the Healer.

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:48.640
' He is still healing the sick today, folks.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:02:05.180
I'm bold about it because I've seen it time and time again that He's doing it.

00:02:10.051 --> 00:02:10.429
We have to take it by faith.

00:02:10.429 --> 00:02:29.420
You've got to reach out and grab the hem of His garment by faith and call those things that be not as though they were.

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:56.900
I'm excited about that; I just wanted to give God praise, a testimony, and a shout of glory because He is doing miracles through this YouTube channel.

00:02:56.900 --> 00:03:00.537
I'm believing for your manifestation.

00:03:01.783 --> 00:03:12.031
There's a gentleman named Keith, and for his privacy's sake, his last name starts with an R.

00:03:12.031 --> 00:03:21.530
He writes us well-written letters that bless me every single time.

00:03:37.544 --> 00:03:38.888
He is just so awesome in the way he talks about his family and everything he's going through.

00:03:38.888 --> 00:04:00.449
He's an elderly gentleman, but we look forward to him writing to us because we've kept every single one; they are very precious to us.

00:04:00.449 --> 00:04:08.840
He is asking for his children to come home to the Lord.

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:24.429
They are very liberal and need a touch, so I'm going to believe God with him today.

00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:40.840
I felt the cry for the children to come home in that letter, and it really moved me today when I got it.

00:04:41.965 --> 00:04:51.576
The Lord was showing me there are so many of you that have children who are wayward.

00:05:00.724 --> 00:05:13.229
You feel like you're at the end of your rope sometimes, feeling that there's no hope because they are so lost and it seems so far out there.

00:05:13.229 --> 00:05:22.874
When you're at the end of the rope, Jesus has grabbed onto the rope with you.

00:05:33.629 --> 00:05:33.960
When all else is done, stand therefore.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:48.854
I just want to encourage every single one of you: do not give up on your unsaved loved ones.

00:05:48.854 --> 00:06:13.780
When I had my visitation almost over two weeks ago, the Lord told me, 'You must pray for the blinders to come off their eyes and that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened.

00:06:13.780 --> 00:06:28.615
' Satan blinds the eyes of the unbeliever and causes it so that they can't see the light of the truth.

00:06:42.284 --> 00:06:52.657
The Bible says to train up a child in the way they should go, and when they get older, they will not depart from it.

00:06:52.657 --> 00:07:11.000
Regardless, even if they're wayward, they're going to come back because those seeds of truth are planted inside of them.

00:07:15.015 --> 00:07:40.990
You may say, 'I never trained them up in the way they should go,' but it doesn't matter; God's merciful, and I believe we can turn them around by prayer.

00:07:48.326 --> 00:07:58.613
The same Jesus Christ of Nazareth that was raised 2,000 years ago from the dead dwells on the inside of you.

00:07:58.613 --> 00:07:59.653
Do you believe it?

00:07:59.653 --> 00:08:09.950
Do you believe you have power and authority over the devil?

00:08:13.060 --> 00:08:23.440
You might say, 'I believe you do, Brother Brandon,' but do you believe you do?

00:08:23.440 --> 00:08:40.700
He's no respecter of persons; the same Jesus that lives inside of me lives inside of you.

00:08:40.700 --> 00:09:03.640
I'm telling you, we have power and authority over the devil because the Bible tells us we do, so we have to use it today.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:15.103
We cannot just sit there and pray a weak, anemic prayer.

00:09:22.076 --> 00:09:30.795
I believe it's time we get bold about our faith and know that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:09:30.795 --> 00:09:46.240
Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:54.694
Let's get started and pray for the wayward children.

00:09:54.694 --> 00:09:58.080
I'm using Keith R's children as a point of contact for every single one of you.

00:09:58.080 --> 00:10:09.880
When we pray for our brother and take our needs off of ourselves, there's power in prayer.

00:10:15.135 --> 00:10:26.670
You have to take your eyes off the problem and look into Jesus' face because He's the answer.

00:10:26.670 --> 00:10:35.399
He has America, Australia, Canada, and Asia—He has all of it, folks.

00:10:35.399 --> 00:11:06.346
I believe with all my heart we will see the greatest outpouring of the Spirit of God this world has seen yet, and we're going to see a major move of His presence in these last days.

00:11:06.346 --> 00:11:26.675
Father, we just thank You for Keith R's children and we call all these children in right now in the name of Jesus.

00:11:26.675 --> 00:11:39.880
We're going to take communion over it and we say, 'Satan, take your hands off of our children!

00:11:39.880 --> 00:11:45.540
Get your hands off of their eyes!

00:11:45.540 --> 00:12:16.817
' I thank You, Lord, that You said if we call those things that be not as though they were, we say they are saved, they are filled with the Holy Ghost, and they are on fire for Jesus.

00:12:16.817 --> 00:12:26.287
They are no longer wayward, but they are coming home.

00:12:26.287 --> 00:12:37.340
I thank You, Lord, that this is the time for them to get radically born again.

00:12:37.340 --> 00:12:49.933
Father, I thank You that You will not allow any of our children to go to hell.

00:12:49.933 --> 00:12:57.519
We stand in that gap interceding for them.

00:12:57.519 --> 00:13:22.734
Angels, I thank You that You're going on behalf of each and every person that has wayward children, and we call forth the mighty hand of the Lord to move right now.

00:13:22.734 --> 00:13:31.480
We call forth results: first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation.

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:39.930
It's time for a great acceleration when it comes to wayward children coming home.

00:13:39.930 --> 00:13:52.829
Every person represented here today who has wayward children, we say they are not wayward anymore.

00:13:52.829 --> 00:14:03.884
They are saved, filled with the Holy Ghost, and on fire for You, Lord.

00:14:03.884 --> 00:14:17.200
We take authority over those blinders and say that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened.

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:42.416
I call them in, and I call the Lord of the harvest to bring in those children, relatives, husbands, or wayward wives.

00:14:42.416 --> 00:14:46.040
No more, Satan!

00:15:02.377 --> 00:15:02.874
You will not have our loved ones.

00:15:08.440 --> 00:15:12.885
We call the hardness of their hearts to be pliable and soft to the gospel.

00:15:14.019 --> 00:15:21.305
We thank You, Lord, that they're calling today and saying, 'Mom, Dad, I am coming home.

00:15:21.305 --> 00:15:25.623
I want to be born again.

00:15:25.623 --> 00:15:47.870
I see the error in my ways and I know I've been wrong and I've been wayward and today I want to turn around and repent.

00:15:47.870 --> 00:15:56.829
' I stand in agreement with every single one of you.

00:15:56.829 --> 00:16:02.104
Father, we take communion over it.

00:16:02.104 --> 00:16:24.860
You're a healer and a deliverer, and You will bring those wayward family members home because their eyes are open and they know the error in their ways.

00:16:24.860 --> 00:16:29.970
They don't want to go to hell.

00:16:29.970 --> 00:16:50.396
May they have an inward shaking experience with the Holy Spirit to wake them up in the middle of the night.

00:16:50.396 --> 00:16:58.260
I thank You, Lord, for angelic visitations and manifestations of angelic beings.

00:16:58.260 --> 00:17:18.026
I thank You, Lord, that as we take this body, we're believing by faith that You're bringing all of our kids home.

00:17:18.026 --> 00:17:26.559
We take it by faith that we're healed and whole.

00:17:40.577 --> 00:17:41.810
No viruses will come nigh us this winter—no flu, no pestilence, no plagues, no nothing comes nigh us, Father.

00:17:41.810 --> 00:17:51.110
We walk in divine health—no respiratory issues, colds, or sinus infections.

00:17:51.110 --> 00:18:15.119
For You were wounded for our transgressions, You were bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon You, and with Your stripes we are healed.

00:18:16.745 --> 00:18:20.695
I call forth new hearts, even for Sherry.

00:18:37.031 --> 00:18:37.302
I thank You, Lord, for a creative miracle in Sherry's heart even with that pacemaker.

00:18:42.735 --> 00:18:44.691
We speak to that heart: be healed in the name of Jesus!

00:18:44.691 --> 00:19:02.820
Sherry, from the top of your head to the souls of your feet, no more of this fear and torment over you anymore.

00:19:10.728 --> 00:19:16.954
We take authority over that demonic spirit whispering in your ear and command it to go now!

00:19:18.440 --> 00:19:38.377
The Lord says to fill your mind and spirit with His Word and meditate on it like you would take medicine.

00:19:38.377 --> 00:19:53.307
Meditate on His Word until it becomes Rhema in your spirit and the breakthrough is there.

00:19:58.411 --> 00:20:05.044
The heart is related to fear and meditation on the wrong things.

00:20:05.044 --> 00:20:16.742
Meditate on the Word so you know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:20:17.533 --> 00:20:39.109
But you've got to get the heart lined up with the Word, because the Bible says that men's hearts will fail them for fear looking at those things coming upon the Earth.

00:20:39.109 --> 00:20:48.160
You've got to get fear out, for fear tolerated is faith contaminated.

00:20:48.160 --> 00:21:01.185
You've got to get the Word in to transform the fear you've been meditating on.

00:21:01.185 --> 00:21:24.487
It may take having less time on social media and YouTube, but getting the Word down inside is more important because His words are life to those that find them and health to all their flesh.

00:21:24.487 --> 00:21:49.040
Sherry, you've got to get this down there and turn the ship around because the Lord still has a work for you to do.

00:21:57.154 --> 00:21:57.859
Do not have fear about what's coming upon the Earth.

00:21:57.859 --> 00:22:08.700
Don't take thought for tomorrow, for tomorrow will have worries of its own.

00:22:08.700 --> 00:22:32.719
Spend time with Him, for if you abide in Him and His words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done for you.

00:22:32.719 --> 00:22:43.575
Father, I thank You for the covenant, and Your promises are yes and amen.

00:22:46.120 --> 00:22:50.450
I call forth healing over these bodies, hearts, and minds.

00:22:50.450 --> 00:23:05.550
We call those things to be not as though they were, and we are well: spirit, soul, and body.

00:23:05.550 --> 00:23:10.620
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:23:10.620 --> 00:23:21.860
If we make much of the blood, the blood will make much of us.

00:23:21.860 --> 00:23:28.000
We take the care out of our prayer.

00:23:28.285 --> 00:23:33.418
You told us to be careful for nothing.

00:23:33.418 --> 00:23:45.244
We trust in the finished work of Jesus Christ that He will bring them home.

00:24:00.000 --> 00:24:00.453
We take this blood right now and call them in.

00:24:01.813 --> 00:24:13.107
We thank You, Father, that this will be the greatest miracle-working year.

00:24:13.107 --> 00:24:28.480
We call for peace in the home, a time of heaven on earth in your homes.

00:24:28.480 --> 00:24:44.765
Having peace in the home is like winning the lottery; there's not a price tag on it.

00:24:44.765 --> 00:25:03.320
We apply the blood over your children today; we apply the blood over your husbands and your wives today.

00:25:03.320 --> 00:25:21.999
We apply the blood of Jesus over people who are tormented in the mind, tormented with depression or satanic bondage.

00:25:24.920 --> 00:25:31.289
We renew our minds with the word of God.

00:25:43.101 --> 00:26:07.520
You have to have a foundation of the word of God down inside of your heart so that when the waves and the winds of life come and your house is planted upon the Rock, your house will stand the test of the storm.

00:26:07.520 --> 00:26:20.980
Prayer alone won't do it; it's the Word that will set the captives free.

00:26:20.980 --> 00:26:34.566
Read the Word and listen to people like Brother Hagin or John Kilpatrick who preach the word.

00:26:34.566 --> 00:26:40.760
You've got to get angry at the devil.

00:26:52.240 --> 00:26:52.529
You can't be passive about a devil that's trying to kill you.

00:26:52.529 --> 00:27:00.980
If you give him an inch, he'll take a mile.

00:27:06.343 --> 00:27:11.279
Jesus is coming, and you better get your lamps filled with oil.

00:27:22.331 --> 00:27:23.086
Lord, we apply the blood over us.

00:27:23.086 --> 00:27:47.293
This bottle of olive oil with rosemary and frankincense is significant in the spirit realm when used by faith.

00:27:47.293 --> 00:27:53.753
I anoint my children with oil before they go to school.

00:28:02.959 --> 00:28:03.199
I plead the blood of Jesus over them.

00:28:04.123 --> 00:28:11.690
I anoint their noses and mouths so no virus enters.

00:28:20.155 --> 00:28:20.337
We are covered in this house by the blood.

00:28:20.337 --> 00:32:13.940
I anoint their minds; they have the mind of Christ and can do all things through Christ who strengthens them.

00:32:13.950 --> 00:35:39.200
Megan is getting better and better; I see the fruit there.

00:35:39.200 --> 00:35:43.520
Glory to God!

00:35:43.520 --> 00:39:08.330
She's turning around and one day she will give her testimony on here.

00:39:08.330 --> 00:39:40.583
She will go viral in the name of Jesus, testifying that Jesus is the healer.

00:39:40.583 --> 00:39:57.220
Anoint your bedposts.

00:40:09.264 --> 00:40:12.387
If you have a husband or wife who is in sin, anoint their pillow and headboard and pray over them in their sleep.

00:40:12.387 --> 00:40:30.800
Apply the blood over your car, doorposts, and windows.

00:40:30.800 --> 00:40:40.280
No calamity shall come nigh you.

00:40:40.280 --> 00:40:54.537
Father, we pray for America.

00:40:54.537 --> 00:41:14.280
It's on my heart today to keep praying for Donald Trump and that all corruption against him would be uncovered.

00:41:14.280 --> 00:42:13.480
Only an awakening under God will save America, and I believe You put Donald J.

00:42:13.480 --> 00:42:19.340
Trump in this position to lead us.

00:42:49.879 --> 00:42:52.160
I pray for supernatural wisdom over his mind and a radical visitation from You, Lord.

00:42:52.160 --> 00:43:01.199
Shake him in the midnight hour and call him to his knees for such a time as this.

00:43:06.840 --> 00:43:22.090
I thank You for a move of Your presence in the White House and supernatural wisdom over President Trump, JD Vance, and all the cabinet members.

00:43:23.880 --> 00:43:25.630
We intercede for other nations too.

00:43:25.630 --> 00:43:34.151
We call for the removal of Justin Trudeau and his evil cabinet.

00:43:46.885 --> 00:43:47.180
We call for the people of Canada to rise up with righteous indignation.

00:43:47.180 --> 00:43:51.890
Satan, you will not take Canada anymore!

00:43:51.890 --> 00:44:14.057
We thank You for raising up men and women of God to take back what the enemy has stolen in Australia, England, France, Europe, Asia, and Africa.

00:44:14.057 --> 00:44:23.234
This world will see a move of the Spirit like never before.

00:44:23.234 --> 00:44:30.690
Rise up and know who you are in Father.

00:44:30.690 --> 00:44:34.600
Be bold about your faith.

00:44:44.068 --> 00:44:44.400
Thank You, Lord, for healings and deliverances.

00:44:48.783 --> 00:44:52.486
I believe we received what we prayed today.

00:44:55.869 --> 00:44:57.420
If you haven't subscribed, please do.

00:44:57.420 --> 00:45:09.531
If you want something in the natural to change, you have to start in the supernatural.

00:45:09.531 --> 00:45:18.493
You have to take authority over it in the spirit realm first.

00:45:18.493 --> 00:45:28.480
We speak blessing over your households, finances, jobs, and raises.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We are the head and not the tail, above and not beneath.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Amen.
